License-file:        LICENSE
Author:              John Wiegley
Maintainer:          johnw@newartisans.com
Category:            Data, Conduit
Build-type:          Simple
Cabal-version:       >=1.8
Homepage:            http://github.com/jwiegley/simple-conduit

Library
